    <div class="panel panel-default">
<a name="grading"></a>
<div class="panel-heading">Recommendation Requests</div>
<div class="panel-body">
        <p>Recommendation letters may be provided if:</p>

        <ul>
          <li>you have taken two courses with me or if you&#39;ve worked with me in some capacity (grader, tutor, etc.)</li>
          <li>you are applying to a maximum of 4 schools</li>
          <li>your academic performance warrants a recommendation (typically, this means an A in the course)</li>
        </ul>

        <p>To request a recommendation</p>

        <ul>
          <li>schedule an in-person meeting with me</li>
          <li>send me an unofficial transcript and a resume</li>
          <li>send me a letter explaining why you&#39;re applying to the graduate or phd program / program(s) and what makes you a good fit for the program (being more specific is better)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div><!-- end col -->



